A set of test to exercise the data package manager and authorization/authentication.

Prerequisites: ruby 1.9, bundler, sqlite3

To run type:

  - git clone https://github.com/kf8a/tiger
  - cd tiger
  - bundle

Then:

  - Modify the host variable in features/step_definitions/lib/eml.rb to point to the public address on your computer
  - Create a passwords.yaml file, with the usernames and passwords. See passwords.yaml.example for an example.

Finally run:

  - cucumber

And experience sweet success or crushing failure
